headline: Robinhood, IBD Stock Of The Day, Near New Buy Points After 260% Surge In 2025
summary: Robinhood is the IBD Stock Of The Day for Wednesday.  The recent addition to the S&P 500 has rallied 260% this year as it expands its prediction market platform and other offerings.  Robinhood is coming off its Q3 beat from Nov. 5.

headline: Kalshi Wins Temporary Pause Against Connecticut Gambling Order
summary: A federal judge has handed prediction markets platform Kalshi a temporary shield from enforcement after Connecticut regulators accused the company of running unlicensed online gambling.
